"594","<TEXT>"
"595","ITEM 77Q(a) - COPIES OF ALL MATERIAL AMENDMENTS TO THE"
"596","REGISTRANT'S CHARTER OR BY-LAWS"
"597","FEDERATED FIXED INCOME SECURITIES, INC."
"598","ARTICLES SUPPLEMENTARY"
"599","   Federated Fixed Income Securities, Inc., a Maryland"
"600","corporation having its principal office in the City of"
"601","Baltimore, Maryland and a registered open-end Company under the"
"602","Investment Company Act of 1940 (the Corporation), hereby"
"603","certifies to the State Department of Assessments and Taxation of"
"604","Maryland that:"
"605","   FIRST:   The Corporation is authorized to issue ten billion"
"606","(10,000,000,000) shares of common stock, all of which have a par"
"607","value of one tenth of one cent ($.001) per share, with an"
