"821","LIMITED POWER OF ATTORNEY"
"822","   KNOW ALL MEN BY THESE PRESENTS, dated as of June 1, 2017,"
"823","that Federated Fixed Income Securities, Inc., a corporation duly"
"824","organized under the laws of the  state of Maryland (the"
"825","Corporation), does hereby nominate, constitute and appoint the"
"826","Federated Investment Management Company, a business trust duly"
"827","organized under the laws of the state of Delaware (the"
"828","Adviser), to act hereunder as the true and lawful agent and"
"829","attorney-in-fact of the Corporation, acting on behalf of each of"
"830","the series portfolios of the Corporation for which the Adviser"
"831","provides advisory services and acts as investment adviser as of"
"832","the date of this limited power attorney and for such series"
"833","portfolios that may be established by the Corporation in the"
"834","future from time to (each such series portfolio being"
"835","hereinafter referred to as a Fund and collectively as the"
"836","Funds), for the specific purpose of executing and delivering"
"837","all such agreements, instruments, contracts, assignments, bond"
"838","powers, stock powers, transfer instructions, receipts, waivers,"
"839","consents and other documents, and performing all such acts, as"
"840","the Adviser may deem necessary or reasonably desirable, related"
"841","to the acquisition, disposition and/or reinvestment of the funds"
"842","and assets of a Fund of the Corporation in accordance with"
"843","Adviser's supervision of the investment, sale and reinvestment"
"844","of the funds and assets of each Fund pursuant to the authority"
"845","granted to the Adviser as investment adviser of each Fund under"
"846","that certain investment advisory contract dated December 24,"
"847","1991 by and between the Adviser and the Corporation (such"
"848","investment advisory contract, as may be amended, supplemented or"
"849","otherwise modified from time to time is hereinafter referred to"
"850","as the Investment Advisory Contract)."
"851","   The Adviser shall exercise or omit to exercise the powers and"
"852","authorities granted herein in each case as the Adviser in its"
"853","sole and absolute discretion deems desirable or appropriate"
"854","under existing circumstances.  The Corporation hereby ratifies"
"855","and confirms as good and effectual, at law or in equity, all"
"856","that the Adviser, and its officers and employees, may do by"
"857","virtue hereof.  However, despite the above provisions, nothing"
"858","herein shall be construed as imposing a duty on the Adviser to"
"859","act or assume responsibility for any matters referred to above"
"860","or other matters even though the Adviser may have power or"
"861","authority hereunder to do so.  Nothing in this Limited Power of"
"862","Attorney shall be construed (i) to be an amendment or"
"863","modifications of, or supplement to, the Investment Advisory"
"864","Contract, (ii) to amend, modify, limit or denigrate any duties,"
"865","obligations or liabilities of the Adviser under the terms of the"
"866","Investment Advisory Contract or (iii) exonerate, relieve or"
"867","release the Adviser any losses, obligations, penalties, actions,"
"868","judgments and suits and other costs, expenses and disbursements"
"869","of any kind or nature whatsoever which may be imposed on,"
"870","incurred by or asserted against the Adviser (x) under the terms"
"871","of the Investment Advisory Contract or (y) at law, or in equity,"
"872","for the performance of its duties as the investment adviser of"
"873","any of the Funds."
"874","   The Corporation hereby agrees to indemnify and save harmless"
"875","the Adviser and its Directors, officers and employees (each of"
"876","the foregoing an Indemnified Party and collectively the"
"877","Indemnified Parties) against and from any and all losses,"
"878","obligations, penalties, actions, judgments and suits and other"
"879","costs, expenses and disbursements of any kind or nature"
"880","whatsoever which may be imposed on, incurred by or asserted"
"881","against an Indemnified Party, other than as a consequence of"
"882","gross negligence or willful misconduct on the part of an"
"883","Indemnified Party, arising out of or in connection with this"
"884","Limited Power of Attorney or any other agreement, instrument or"
"885","document executed in connection with the exercise of the"
"886","authority granted to the Adviser herein to act on behalf of the"
"887","Corporation, including without limitation the reasonable costs,"
"888","expenses and disbursements in connection with defending such"
"889","Indemnified Party against any claim or liability related to the"
"890","exercise or performance of any of the Adviser's powers or duties"
"891","under this Limited Power of Attorney or any of the other"
"892","agreements, instruments or documents executed in connection with"
"893","the exercise of the authority granted to the Adviser herein to"
"894","act on behalf of the Corporation, or the taking of any action"
"895","under or in connection with any of the foregoing.  The"
"896","obligations of the Corporation under this paragraph shall"
"897","survive the termination of this Limited Power of Attorney with"
"898","respect to actions taken by the Adviser on behalf of the"
"899","Corporation during the term of this Limited Power of Attorney."
"900","No Fund shall have any joint or several obligation with any"
"901","other Fund to reimburse or indemnify an Indemnified Party for"
"902","any action, event, matter or occurrence performed or omitted by"
"903","or on behalf of the Adviser in its capacity as agent or"
"904","attorney-in-fact of Corporation acting on behalf of any other"
"905","Fund hereunder."
"906","   Any person, partnership, Corporation or other legal entity"
"907","dealing with the Adviser in its capacity as attorney-in-fact"
"908","hereunder for the Corporation is hereby expressly put on notice"
"909","that the Adviser is acting solely in the capacity as an agent of"
"910","the Corporation and that any such person, partnership,"
"911","Corporation or other legal entity must look solely to the"
"912","Corporation in question for enforcement of any claim against the"
"913","Corporation, as the Adviser assumes no personal liability"
"914","whatsoever for obligations of the Corporation entered into by"
"915","the Adviser in its capacity as attorney-in-fact for the"
"916","Corporation."
"917","   Each person, partnership, Corporation or other legal entity"
"918","which deals with a Fund of the Corporation through the Adviser"
